he 's the wolf this is not a very tough choice , if you like howlin ' wolf or the blues get this box . it has not weak tracks , some fascinating interviews ( well the wolf talking ) , and many of the classic , indispensable tracks.plus , there 's , as evidenced here , no other electric blues guitarist nearly as nasty , dirty , just downright awesome as hubert sumlin . buy and enjoy , this is the blues at its best